    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“What everyone wants – a piece of the pie. Doesn’t have to be a big one,” Glabrio adds quickly. “Give me Lowtown and I’ll give you Ganezzar.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“And if I say no?”</text>
          <def_link>3</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>[word of honor]“Alright, Lowtown is yours. You have my word.”</text>
          <def_link>4</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>2</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Then neither of us gets what we want,” Glabrio glances at his brethren - rough-looking men standing ready to do violence and looking forward to it.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>[word of honor]“Alright, Lowtown is yours. You have my word.”</text>
          <def_link>4</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>You'd rather fail with honor than win by lying. Kill them and return to Paullus.</text>
          <def_link>8</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
